&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years in test automation, SDET, or software engineering roles with a strong testing focus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong C#/.NET skills — you write production-quality test code, not just record-and-playback scripts&lt;/li&gt;
